{"tid":2454232,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"水原希子公路全裸開寫真展 肉照現澀谷鬧市","createTime":"2021-03-20T05:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T06:27:43.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3d8e4323dfc30bd6d424f9831a59150c6ca91c5a","tid":2454232,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cNvvFVSS2Hb9WUYVBTp379sHRxA=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XWRFLOXCZFE5HOXBMWOBX26U3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcNvvFVSS2Hb9WUYVBTp379sHRxA%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXWRFLOXCZFE5HOXBMWOBX26U3I.jpg&h=1a8ee96f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美韓混血的日籍女星水原希子，作風一向大膽，由她擔正的Netflix電影《彼女》安排下月中起全球上架，水原希子今次挑戰SheShe床戲，更全裸演大膽情慾場面。<br />\n<br />\n水原希子崇尚裸體自然並非新鮮事，她為攝影師好友茂木Monika拍攝公路寫真集《夢之繼續 DREAM BLUE》，由於Monika是希子最信任的攝影師，故今次在美國取景期間也毫不介意戶外全裸，照片是在四年前旅行時拍攝，置身大自然來一次大解放，照片中可看見水原希子裸體出鏡，包括仰躺水中、背對鏡頭坐在路邊，相當有睇頭。<br />\n<br />\n水原希子這輯性感照除以寫真集形式推出外，更會於東京澀谷PARCO位於4樓的PARCO MUSEUM TOKYO辦展覽，由今日起至4月4日為期16天，水原希子與茂木Monika今日均有到現場，更舉行簽名會滿足fans，而澀谷PARCO外更以水原希子的肉照製成巨型廣告，十分搶眼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Mc6nveQj3mwXJL4ZC6xPFnhvZis=/802x1140/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BUCGF2GYENHJRIOJJN7CWXKIQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMc6nveQj3mwXJL4ZC6xPFnhvZis%3D%2F802x1140%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBUCGF2GYENHJRIOJJN7CWXKIQE.jpg&h=863e06d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wDQCxACluQFjJ1BSOuMAWdpEvtE=/802x1156/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AW3BMVRNXRDKVKYBI6ZKJXUYSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwDQCxACluQFjJ1BSOuMAWdpEvtE%3D%2F802x1156%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAW3BMVRNXRDKVKYBI6ZKJXUYSE.jpg&h=fa139720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OOcXpKva0tiZIHqk5K0EGTofmjk=/802x553/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WJF2ATQWXVCM3CIS5AHQ36R7HA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOOcXpKva0tiZIHqk5K0EGTofmjk%3D%2F802x553%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWJF2ATQWXVCM3CIS5AHQ36R7HA.jpg&h=97d5e21c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OkinwOAbSmkhouk4ijr2Qtv4BfY=/802x1146/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WDGV7MIBOZC4ZDSLCB7VDSUP6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOkinwOAbSmkhouk4ijr2Qtv4BfY%3D%2F802x1146%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWDGV7MIBOZC4ZDSLCB7VDSUP6A.jpg&h=14137ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dJ-9TSTf4btwm1NOuFMyUTlBVTs=/802x1152/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XGN37JDIWBHXBNUUV742MRTX6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdJ-9TSTf4btwm1NOuFMyUTlBVTs%3D%2F802x1152%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXGN37JDIWBHXBNUUV742MRTX6U.jpg&h=204b3486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_fP8xesejzNnHSZvKIPLDyFJlJg=/802x1140/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HVUOYQZBCBC7BC5LES47I2H3HM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu